{
  "stem": "4830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, this was a great relief for me, because I always wanted to write.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I did not think that this would be a major difference between me and God.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I told him that, considering the circumstances, I am willing to write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I looked very sad, but in fact I was very happy that this, which I considered was basically an ordeal, was over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because it's difficult to be so different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because in the class we were 49 students.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Out of these 49, about 22 were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But everybody wrote.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the whole school, I was the only one, after my brother left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- and my younger brother, but he was in a Jewish class and they were teaching differently.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I was the only one in the mainstream in this school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I don't know how many others were in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in grade five, this gymnasium, which was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at 15 years of age, I started to write on Saturdays, and I keep writing ever since.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not necessarily on Saturdays, but I make no difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What elements of the Jewish observance remained important to you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only those that my father asked me to observe, and I promised him to observe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] don't really consider the-- the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jewish or any other religion-- the rules as important.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In-- in my opinion, the only thing that counts, not what I pray but what I do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nevertheless, I am observing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father asked me, so I didn't ask him why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he discovered that I am not as religious as he is, he said that, no matter what I think, I should observe [INAUDIBLE] services.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I should [INAUDIBLE] and I should fast in Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
